Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.22,0:00:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會 怎麼能這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.66,0:00:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have control！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.81,0:00:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…你想做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.30,0:00:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.26,0:00:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.47,0:00:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡您了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.35,0:00:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.83,0:00:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.21,0:00:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.80,0:00:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通信嗎？能聽到什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.08,0:00:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 妹子 你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.51,0:00:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.83,0:01:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各島的氣密狀態無變化 生命線正常恢復中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.37,0:01:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像沒有出現市民的死傷者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.95,0:01:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個導航女僕算什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.93,0:01:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底到底是哪兒的傢伙啊 竟然發射那樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.77,0:01:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是從月球基地來的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.61,0:01:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人好像偽裝成被Nerval大人所控制
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.86,0:01:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信能將Kirkwood一舉殲滅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.09,0:01:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題是接下來對方的態度了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.84,0:01:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的人類 攻擊只會找來報復的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.86,0:01:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類是矛盾的集合體
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.62,0:01:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然知道爭鬥不會獲得什麼 但仍然不斷互相傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.86,0:01:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master 要怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.45,0:01:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往讓我們受傷的罪魁禍首處 阻止更大的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.11,0:01:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是對那即使無謀也要保護Kirkwood的那小小的勇氣的回禮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.40,0:01:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸位繼續進行損害狀況的調查
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.49,0:01:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.83,0:01:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫桑齊貝負責獅子堂秋葉的搜查
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.46,0:01:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她應該就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.16,0:02:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.21,0:02:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miss.阿蕾達 你找到奈美了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.91,0:02:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 雖然好像經過了戰鬥 但無大礙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Existent-Z正在護送她前往這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.06,0:02:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miss.高嶺…正在搜索中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.88,0:02:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈美…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.39,0:04:00.27,EDTITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(520,290)}{\fs45}{\fad(500,500)}余冥的路途
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱好熱…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.50,0:04:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獅子堂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊…月？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.34,0:04:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來救我了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.38,0:04:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.22,0:04:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獅子堂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.41,0:04:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獅子堂秋葉被發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我們放下 你們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這好像不行 會長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.65,0:04:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.44,0:04:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於剛才的攻擊 推進單元好像壞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.98,0:04:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法甩開他們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.94,0:04:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.19,0:04:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來只能躲進Kirkwood了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.35,0:04:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.89,0:05:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來沒辦法回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長 這裡好像能進去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 妹子在哪兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子她…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全艦已經做好出發準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.41,0:05:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖覺得有點暴力 但災禍必須在眼前拔除
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.93,0:05:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（外星語？）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.99,0:05:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果消滅了Kirkwood 就沒必要將這區域的再開發權交給其他人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.20,0:06:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著就乘這氣勢佔領各宙域吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.53,0:06:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候只要月球和烏雷進行共同管理就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的慾望真是可悲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.86,0:06:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.98,0:06:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受制裁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.24,0:06:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦…艦隊被凍住了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.34,0:06:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不配被支配 在冰雪之中永遠地長眠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.09,0:07:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杜鵑 你在哪兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.15,0:07:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別藏了 快出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.72,0:07:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底要開玩笑到什麼時候啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子她…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.16,0:07:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討…討厭呢 這種時候就別開玩笑了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊月…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獅子堂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.88,0:07:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.55,0:07:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊月也是 學生會長也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.78,0:08:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰給藏起來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.77,0:08:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把妹子放出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.14,0:08:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在騙我吧 伊月
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.20,0:08:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…她剛剛還在我身邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一直都在的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.53,0:08:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從此以後也會…一直在一起的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.77,0:08:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約好了的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約好一起吃飛碟燒的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.60,0:08:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獅子堂…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.64,0:08:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是真的！這不是真的啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.13,0:08:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們再早點到達的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快說這不是真的…伊月
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.50,0:08:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.66,0:08:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.44,0:09:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.28,0:09:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.78,0:09:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就到印斯茅斯暗礁了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.57,0:09:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷歐帕羅特 將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.85,0:09:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不認同 剛才的不算
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.75,0:09:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 下局我要認真了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:09:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下局是第幾局了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.26,0:10:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是第121局 剛才正好是風音小姐的120連勝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.11,0:10:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你適可而止吧 雷歐帕羅特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.12,0:10:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣你也太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.16,0:10:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什什什…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.48,0:10:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去 別說Nerval你連庫桑齊貝都贏不了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.48,0:10:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那和這遊戲有什麼關係？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.99,0:10:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不好好幹的話 我會很困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.87,0:10:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是比賽的話 就得全贏才行！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.63,0:10:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明和Nerval的決戰就在眼前了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.15,0:10:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不是已經承認你的回收計劃了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.61,0:10:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為僅僅改變外在就能贏嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.69,0:10:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果沒了秋葉的協助…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.97,0:10:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就趕快把枯葉帶過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋葉的話 交給伊月她們就沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你能這麼說？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.13,0:10:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和這個棋子一樣 人和物都有各自的發揮領域
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.99,0:10:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可別把偉大的我當做是物品什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對Nerval戰略的構築怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.99,0:11:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集完和庫桑齊貝的戰鬥數據之後就完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個會在不遠的將來到手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.94,0:11:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.21,0:11:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱子人 被Nerval囚禁起來的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.01,0:11:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是第一次看到這麼多聚集在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.30,0:11:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 有人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽不見嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼做才能救他們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.39,0:11:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獅子堂 你曾經呆在箱子裡過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.24,0:11:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 你不就應該知道什麼方法嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.84,0:11:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！說點什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.98,0:11:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別這樣 獅子堂可是剛剛失去了妹子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你既是地球孤兒的話 也明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.91,0:11:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人被奪走的那種痛苦…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.23,0:12:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是那個叫Nerval的傢伙正在幹的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 麻煩的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.56,0:12:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.09,0:12:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這邊 別再把騷動升級了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.73,0:12:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那制服 蘇爾學園的自由等級嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.35,0:12:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.88,0:12:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個女孩…這不是秋葉大小姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馮？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就想著你的壽命也差不多該到頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.31,0:12:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馮 是你救了我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.64,0:13:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是QT-Rose有反應了而已 跟我沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 回去時小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.82,0:13:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.44,0:13:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了在宇宙等著你 但是你卻沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.93,0:13:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,QT-Rose的促生栽培術也完成了 我之前還在想這就上宇宙的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.13,0:13:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你一催我又不想去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.97,0:13:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有我的時間安排 將其踐踏的沒神經的人…啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.11,0:13:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從一開始就應該這麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.99,0:13:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,QT-Rose的種植場呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.46,0:14:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在…地下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.48,0:14:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enigma同盟？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.47,0:14:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是以前曾與Nerval戰鬥過的叛亂軍倖存者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.58,0:14:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們就是「獅子堂元老院」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你調查的真清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.11,0:14:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…你們為什麼會在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們被Nerval的同夥襲擊了 逃到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.15,0:14:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個區域是哪兒？這個地方記錄裡沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.97,0:14:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.20,0:14:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賀統 今天的東西運到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.80,0:14:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.50,0:14:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…把裡面的東西取出來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.46,0:14:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面的人死亡了的箱子 就在這裡集中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.11,0:14:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是個巨大的殯儀館嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:14:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個箱子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.78,0:15:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱子人的最後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.71,0:15:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.72,0:15:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那紅箱子能和配戴者的大腦皮層產生共鳴 從而引起QT反應
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.64,0:15:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原料就是死者的腦與神經細胞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.68,0:15:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡趣味啊 Bad tasty
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.36,0:15:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 也是很有效率的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.78,0:15:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nerval不會做無謂的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.23,0:15:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該感慨這些嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 神風？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.27,0:15:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的雙親…說不定…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.32,0:15:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始吧 矢藏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.84,0:15:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BE13KQ07L4556
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.12,0:15:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 還活著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.58,0:15:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假冒成死者讓他們逃脫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 讓箱子醬逃出來的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.24,0:15:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱子醬？啊 那個女孩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:16:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是事先潛伏在Nerval裡的我們的同志的所作所為
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.28,0:16:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.84,0:16:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我們到達這裡的時候 已經成為這樣了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.06,0:16:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.36,0:16:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡即使有一個人也能拯救很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.55,0:16:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是繼承他們精神的我們的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.35,0:16:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 秋葉小姐請來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.03,0:16:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.99,0:16:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲裡奧 音音子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.47,0:16:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你是誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.64,0:16:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神風…不 我是下山睦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱…箱子在哪裡啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.49,0:16:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱子…我想回箱子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱子 箱子…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.59,0:17:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面…好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.19,0:17:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 大家 我們來救你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.45,0:17:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裡逃出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.80,0:17:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.32,0:17:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被箱子奪去心智時 就會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.99,0:17:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋葉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.21,0:17:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能原諒 Nerval必須被打倒！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.41,0:17:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在出現更多被害者之前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.78,0:17:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是這種心情 Angry
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.56,0:17:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賀統 果然是「骸」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.90,0:17:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「骸」…是什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.55,0:17:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微發生了點奇怪的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.77,0:17:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱子能提供給人類所需的所有東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.90,0:17:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓人更健康地生活下去而完美地管理著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.45,0:17:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理論上來說進入箱子後會活得更長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.02,0:18:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不管箱子的機能有沒有異常 原因不明的死者出現的太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.24,0:18:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們叫做「骸」的 就是指的這事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.49,0:18:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說箱子裡發生了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.91,0:18:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不是你們應該知道的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獅子堂秋葉 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.67,0:18:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 被發現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.56,0:18:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 這邊走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.28,0:18:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點乘上去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.92,0:18:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 快點走 快走！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.15,0:18:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點！ 點乘上去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏魯 獅子堂就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.15,0:18:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊月
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.18,0:18:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡由我來阻擋！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:18:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.99,0:19:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.73,0:19:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你們跑的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.99,0:19:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是時候放棄…啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.11,0:19:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…波拿帕羅特嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那是…夥伴！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弁慶 杜鵑 我是神風
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.70,0:19:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你們立即回收我們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.68,0:19:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？啊 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你不是弁慶嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫…庫桑齊貝？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.43,0:19:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想對那些人做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.66,0:19:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.47,0:20:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才多久沒見 你不會就叛變到叛亂軍去了吧？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.01,0:20:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？怎麼會有那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉…閉上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.99,0:20:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.45,0:20:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼啊？這個笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.75,0:20:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起 身體擅自…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.20,0:20:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 跟我預計的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.61,0:20:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事啊 杜鵑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.79,0:20:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這人啊 我稍微把視線移開就變得如此優柔寡斷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.02,0:20:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不 這個是…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.13,0:20:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個小鬼是誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.57,0:20:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弁慶 把這個煩人的人工智能殖民地排除掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？但是 庫桑齊貝是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.91,0:20:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉她！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.33,0:21:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.40,0:21:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你迄今為止都在哪裡啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個 快點把門打開
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.03,0:21:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了接收 在唾沫還沒乾之前就翻臉不認帳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想給我的帝國抹黑嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.55,0:21:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也給我知道下什麼叫羞恥吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.62,0:21:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.69,0:21:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 門…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.76,0:21:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說帝國？沒異想天開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.48,0:21:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區的人類！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.38,0:21:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 打來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.26,0:21:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擋住它！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.07,0:21:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.67,0:21:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ravana？高嶺嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.69,0:21:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長老？為什麼會在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.06,0:21:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳躍！前往印斯茅斯暗礁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.22,0:22:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 老子不管了！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.93,0:22:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…雷歐帕羅特！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.23,0:22:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 真hard啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.72,0:22:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獅子堂 我們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.64,0:22:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹…子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.85,0:24:14.80,EDTITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(522,310)}密劍、閃光
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.03,0:24:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請把伊月小姐嫁給我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.03,0:24:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時雨boy！說的簡單 你年收入是多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.01,0:24:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Level.Free？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.13,0:24:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說freelancer（自由職業者）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.73,0:24:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等於「不安」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.82,0:24:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行呢 貧窮上班族
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.28,0:02:31.38,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡はいつでもそばにある
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.40,0:02:41.36,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輝きたいよ　未来へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.37,0:02:57.32,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたの中　騒めくノイズは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:03:04.94,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馴れ愛の束縛　動けない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.82,0:03:11.76,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦しみが散らばる世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.79,0:03:16.99,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探して　失い、また求めて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.86,0:03:22.94,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辿って　わたしの糸を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:26.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡は必然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.99,0:03:34.79,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そっと抱いてあげる　一雫の痛みも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.80,0:03:40.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯った証が　星になる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.77,0:03:47.13,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扉をあけて　飛べるよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.28,0:02:31.38,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡一直就在我們身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.40,0:02:41.36,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們想要發光 照亮未來…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.37,0:02:57.32,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你心中的 凌亂的雜音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:03:04.94,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是已熟知的愛的束縛 …動彈不得
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.82,0:03:11.76,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦遍佈著這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.79,0:03:16.99,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋找著… 失去，然後再次追求
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.86,0:03:22.94,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追溯吧 沿著我的軌跡…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:26.95,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡必然會發生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.99,0:03:34.79,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄地將你抱住 不讓你有一點疼痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.80,0:03:40.75,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點亮的證明 成為了恆星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.77,0:03:47.13,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開門扉吧… 飛向天空！

Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.47,0:22:45.70,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甦る痛みに流されながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.71,0:22:54.58,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷徨って僕らはどこへ行くんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.60,0:23:08.89,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懐かしく暖かな空　その眩しい景色へ描いた幻は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.90,0:23:15.54,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揺れて消えた　遠く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.95,0:23:25.15,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解けぬ孤独を抱きながら　それでも祈ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.18,0:23:33.78,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰が同じ　希望の訪れが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.86,0:23:41.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闇の破片が　絶えず僕の　胸に突き刺さる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.15,0:23:51.04,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君という光　ただ　知りたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.47,0:22:45.70,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在甦醒的痛苦中隨波逐流
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.71,0:22:54.58,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷徨的我們不知要去往何方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.60,0:23:08.89,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那令人懷念地溫暖地天空 那種炫目地景色描繪出來的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.90,0:23:15.54,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搖擺不定地消失 在遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.95,0:23:25.15,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使被無法擺脫的孤獨抱住 我們也要祈禱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.18,0:23:33.78,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都一樣 希望總會到來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.86,0:23:41.13,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗的碎片 無休止地 刺向我的胸口
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.15,0:23:51.04,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想瞭解以你為名的光芒
